      "raw_text": "The Chelan Transportation &\nSmelling company is actively engag-\ned on the work in connection with\nthe erection of smelter on Railroad\ncreek.\n\n\nThe smslter will have a capacity\nof 500 tons daily and the company\nhas contract with the Holden Gold\ng. Copper Mining company both for\nhauling and smelling the ores.\n\n\nThe work of constructing the\npmelter will begin about April l."
